There have got be some good reasons to be a troll sk.  I have seen alot of slams on the boards against being a troll sk.  I was trying to do some research and was hoping to see some positive posts on trolls...alas it seems troll sk's arent speaking up much.  Could I get some positive advice on trolls as sk's?  I like the regen and the look of trolls.  The starting stats seem to do well for me.  Well, mostly wanted to give atleast somewhat of a positive point for those considering trolls as sk's.

