Why not?  Play what you like.

Ok, so the trolls got kicked out of their swamp by a bunch of hoppers and had to move in with the dark elves who don't particularly like them.  It happens.

They did pick up some newbie quests along the way.  Nektulos isn't so bad.  Lavastorm isn't either, and is typically a wide-open zone for a youngish troll to explore.

With books now, faction and newbie zones are largely a problem of the past.  You can hunt anywhere until your packs are full, book up to PoK, sell off, and book back down.

